cc:Work.dc:title: Little Miss Muffet Poster
cc:Work.dc:description:
Poster promoting reading among children. "Little Miss Muffet / Sat on a tuffet / Reading a picture book / There came a spider / And sat down beside her / And said, 'May I have a look?'" 
 
Source: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Little_Miss_Muffet_1940_poster.jpg (public domain)
